1.6.0
- Now requires DRF version 3.1 or newer.
- Updated Travis CI conf run tests using tox

1.5.0
-----
- Added the ability to place cookies on the proxied request.

1.4.0
-----
- Pass through args and kwargs to the `proxy` method.
- Added testing infrastructure.

1.3.0
-----
- Optionally override SSL verification setting
- Allow empty sources (request goes directly to the host)
- Fixed POST requests when using json payload
- Do not automatically prepend trailing slash to proxy request

1.2.0
-----
- Python 3 support
- Accept-Language header was set incorrectly

1.1.0
-----
- Streaming upload support added

1.0.0
-----
- Initial release
